Survey Discovery

View a list of all available/active surveys
Filter surveys by category, date, or status
Search functionality for finding specific surveys


Survey Participation

Access individual surveys without requiring registration
Answer different question types (multiple choice, text input, rating scales)
Progress indicator showing completion status
Ability to save and resume surveys (optional)


Results Viewing

View survey results if admin has enabled public results
Real-time or near real-time result updates
Visual representations (charts, graphs) of survey data.



